{
  "stem": "24364.3",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "However, they-- since they punishing us, obviously, for what we had done, so they stuck us again into the bunker or the catacombs.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And it was terrible.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "My god.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "I remember that first night.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "There was barely room.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "We were lying on the floor, and there was barely room between the two people.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "It was unbearably hot.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "I will never forget that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "This-- this was, I think, worse, almost worse, than the storm on the Atlantic.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "We couldn't breathe there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "There were like maybe 100 people, you know, stuffed together in one room, which I don't know how big it was.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "But it certainly was not big enough for the amount of people who were there.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "So that's where we slept.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] continued to be punished.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "The next morning, they shaved all the men's hair.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "And they cropped the women's hair completely short, telling us that they wanted-- didn't want any lice.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "But there was really no particular reason, because we had been in Atlit for a week or 10 days, and we were perfectly clean.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "But as I said, they wanted to punish us.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] It was pretty hot also on the boat, because we weren't allowed to go on deck for the first several days.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "And I remember the only thing that we wanted was water.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "And the water was very warm.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "And it was very difficult to get ice water, but sometimes we managed to get a little ice.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "The crew was very nice.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "They mainly Malaysian.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "And some, I think, Filipinos were there, too.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "But they were very nice to us and really tried to help if they could.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "I mean, they couldn't do very much.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "But they brought us some water sometimes.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
